column5: Im there,for a short time,but for a good time.  Reminds me of a song I once heard,,,LOL

For those that missed it,I learned that Gerritts brother is really GCD son (you need to wash that boys mouth out with soap lol),and Beans fell off his chair due to the high winds.Thats how he lost his chair .Johnny Bass ,well he was just snooping around for hot spots for big perch.Dapluma,well he stunk the joint out,so we sent him off for a shower along with Parker,well not together.LOL  Thanks lads for the fun.Off to eat and then it,s bed time.3:30 AM comes WAY TO SOON.  Have a great weekend all.
